Clean, shiny new hotel with spacious welcoming lobby and attractive decor.	Great to stay in a new hotel, very clean, lovely furnishings and decor.	I used to stay at the full service Hilton on Rishmond, but I prefer the low key ambience of this Hilton brand.	The pool and spa were much appreciated as was the Marquis dining room where we had a great breakfast in a relaxed atmosphere.	Breakfast was included with the room and it is served on the second floor as a hot buffet breakfast style.	They use industrial-style elevators to move your car to lower floors, so trained operators are needed.	The room was clean and comfortable with modern decor.